      "title": "Bangladesh\u2019s Mushfiqur retires from T20",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Veteran Bangladesh cricketer Mushfiqur Rahim has announced his retirement from T20 International cricket.",
        "Bangladesh recently fell out of 2022 Asia Cup, while Sri Lanka emerged as the winners of the match, qualifying for the Super Four stage of Asia Cup 2022.",
        "However, Rahim had said that he will continue playing ODIs and test cricket matches representing Bangladesh in the future."
      ],
